description: When the walking dead rise, your only defense is a truly delicious burger! Grill of the Dead is here to stop the zombie hordes with hot, fresh, fantastic burgers. Prepare yourself with their signature burgers like The Winchester, the World War B, or the spicy Dia de los Muertos! For the bets food, and the best chance of survival in town, visit the Grill of the Dead today!
name: Grill of the Dead
